notes: Record partnership for ODI's between Sohail and Inzamam (263)

milestones.description: Wasim Akram has broken the record for most sixes (46) in ODIs for PAK, going past Imran Khan's 45
Aamer Sohail and Inzamam-ul-Haq's 263-run partnership is the highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 221 between Greenidge and Viv Richards
Inzamam-ul-Haq's 137 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for PAK), surpassing Saeed Anwar's 131
Aamer Sohail and Inzamam-ul-Haq's 263-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 205 between Zaheer Abbas and Mohsin Khan
This is the highest match aggregate (594) involving teams New Zealand & Pakistan in ODIs
Aamer Sohail and Inzamam-ul-Haq's 263-run partnership is PAK's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 205 between Mohsin Khan and Zaheer Abbas
Aamer Sohail and Inzamam-ul-Haq's 263-run partnership is the highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 224 between Dean Jones and Allan Border
